Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:00:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:00:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\fs12}So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我被抢劫了\N{\fs12}Ah, I got robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs12}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还行  我是说  缝了几针  还有一根肋骨断了\N{\fs12}Yeah. I mean, a couple stitches and a... broken rib.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我和凯特去了卡拉布里亚  把她安顿好\N{\fs12}I went to Calabria's with Kate. Dropped her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,给个晚安吻\N{\fs12}Good night kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,准备度过这个夜晚  不过  呃  我最后出去喝了一杯\N{\fs12}Was gonna spend the night, but, uh...I ended up going out for a drink after,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  然后在我回车上的时候\N{\fs12}and-- and on my way back to my car,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一个家伙  不知道哪里跳出来的\N{\fs12}some guy, outta nowhere, jumps me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  在我清醒之前带着我的钱包就跑了\N{\fs12}and-- and before I know it, just ran off with my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你有看清楚他吗\N{\fs12}Did you get a look at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  没有  没有  那天  太  太晚了\N{\fs12}Uh, no, no. It was... it was... it was late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你去了哪家酒吧\N{\fs12}What bar did you go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  我忘了  是一个在北边的酒吧\N{\fs12}Oh, I don't know. Some bar on the North Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  如果  如果你不介意  也许  呃\N{\fs12}You know, if-- if you don't mind, maybe, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我可以自己告诉大家我发生了什么\N{\fs12}maybe I'll tell people at work what happened myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:02:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不会说的\N{\fs12}I won't say a word about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 早  - 早上好\N{\fs12}- Morning. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗  谢谢\N{\fs12}How are ya? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  克肯达尔先生  很高兴再见到你\N{\fs12}Ah, Mr. Kirkendall, nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,克肯达尔在等了\N{\fs12}KirkendalI's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  他来早了\N{\fs12}I know. He's early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  他总是很早\N{\fs12}Oh, he's always early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对  杰克还没来吗\N{\fs12}Yeah. Is Jake here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  他  呃  有一个\N{\fs12}I don't know. He, uh... had a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他  他可能会晚一点到\N{\fs12}He... he might be running a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 早\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你是见鬼了吗\N{\fs12}What the hell happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  昨晚小跑的时候\N{\fs12}Uh... had a little... run-in last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有个家伙  呃  我  我  我正往车子那儿走  然后他  把我抢了\N{\fs12}Some guy, uh... l-- l... I was walking to my car, and he... robbed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧  - 没有  我没事\N{\fs12}- You all right? - Yeah. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  是不是  我们是不是应该开始了\N{\fs12}Uh, shouldn't... shouldn't we be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  丹马克还不在\N{\fs12}Ah, Denmar's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,丹马克还没来\N{\fs12}Denmar's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,克肯达尔想解雇他\N{\fs12}Kirkendall wants to fire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他要解雇丹马克吗\N{\fs12}He's firing Denmar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他创立了公司\N{\fs12}He founded the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对  他上个月还花了三千美元\N{\fs12}Yeah, and he also spent about three grand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在某个绅士俱乐部招待了客户\N{\fs12}at some gentlemen's club last month entertaining clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他主张那是商务支出\N{\fs12}Then he submitted it as a business expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他打算为去了脱衣舞夜总会而解雇他吗\N{\fs12}So he's gonna fire him for going to a strip club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对  - 他想利用这个事情\N{\fs12}- Yeah. - And he wants to use this as cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他可以\N{\fs12}lf he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那\N{\fs12}Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  让我  呃  和尼古拉斯聊一会\N{\fs12}Jake, let me, uh, talk to Nicholas a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听着  我  呃  想让杰克处理这件事  - 为什么\N{\fs12}- Listen, l, uh, want Jake to handle this. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,克肯达尔是个保守的人\N{\fs12}Kirkendall, he's a conservative guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对  所以呢\N{\fs12}Right. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  他有着  和你一样的问题\N{\fs12}Well, he's got problems... with your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 好\N{\fs12}- Fine. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你没事吗\N{\fs12}You sure you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对  是的  - 好\N{\fs12}- Yeah. Yeah. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  菲尼  你好吗\N{\fs12}Hey, Finn. How ya doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  伯顿  - 你好\N{\fs12}- Hey, Burton. - Good to see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得杰克·斯特拉卡吧\N{\fs12}You remember Jake Straka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,记得  记得  你没事吧  杰克\N{\fs12}Sure. Sure. How ya been, Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  没事  没事\N{\fs12}Oh, good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的眼睛怎么了\N{\fs12}- What happened to your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢  - 抱歉打扰了\N{\fs12}- Oh-- - I'm sorry to interrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  呃  有个男的  说是刑警想找你谈谈\N{\fs12}but, uh... there's a man... a detective who wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我马上去\N{\fs12}Right. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  抱歉失陪一下\N{\fs12}Uh... excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我可没干什么违法的事  我向你保证\N{\fs12}Uhm... I'm innocent of all charges, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信  对\N{\fs12}I'm sure. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧  菲尼\N{\fs12}Sit down, Finn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的他昨晚被抢了\N{\fs12}Poor guy got mugged last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧  那太糟了\N{\fs12}You're kidding. That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管他是个硬朗的汉子  他会没事的\N{\fs12}He's a tough kid, though. He'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想了解一些事情\N{\fs12}I just want to follow up on a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们在汽车旅馆谈论的时候\N{\fs12}When we talked at the motel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你说那个男人在你开门的时候把你推进了房间是吗\N{\fs12}you said the man pushed you into the room while you were opening the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你没有和他一起\N{\fs12}So you weren't with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是  呃  在停车场闲逛吗\N{\fs12}He was just, uh... roaming around in the parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  我  我不知道\N{\fs12}Oh... l... I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么会在汽车旅馆\N{\fs12}Why were you at the motel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么意思  - 你住镇上  不是吗\N{\fs12}- Excuse me? - You live in town, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我只是奇怪  为什么你要在途中停留在某个汽车旅馆\N{\fs12}So I'm just wondering... why you would stay at some motel on Route 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我  我  你知道  我喝多了\N{\fs12}Well, l... l... you know, I'd had a lot to drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我不想开车回家  原因很明显\N{\fs12}and, uh, I didn't want to drive home for... for obvious reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我决定待在汽车旅馆\N{\fs12}and so I decided to stay in a motel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  医疗报告显示有些撕裂伤口和擦伤\N{\fs12}Uh... medical report says that there were lacerations and abrasions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的腿部和腹股沟部\N{\fs12}in your leg and groin area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想弄明白你的腿是怎么弄伤的  而且你知道\N{\fs12}I'm just trying to understand how you got cuts on your legs and, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是你被突然袭击了  这说不通啊\N{\fs12}lf you got jumped, it doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你知道  那是场打斗\N{\fs12}Hey, you know, it was a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就是碰巧\N{\fs12}Stuff happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对  - 对\N{\fs12}- Right. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道有些事情谈论起来会难受\N{\fs12}I know it's tough to talk about certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我能理解\N{\fs12}I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 感谢您的配合  - 噢  我很乐意\N{\fs12}- Thanks for your time. - Oh, my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fs12}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你怎么样\N{\fs12}Hey, how ya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不好不坏\N{\fs12}Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,打赌你做的双份拿铁一定比卢克好\N{\fs12}Bet you a double latte you're doing better than Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:06:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,什么鬼\N{\fs12}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他碰见了他妈妈和他最好的朋友\N{\fs12}He walked in on his mother and his best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在卧室里接吻  然后  卢克疯了\N{\fs12}They were in the bedroom kissing, and... Luke went nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拿起台灯痛打了他的朋友  还打了他的妈妈\N{\fs12}Grabbed a lamp and beat up his friend. Hit his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,打坏了一些东西\N{\fs12}Broke some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,警察把他抓了起来  叫了我  然后我们就在这儿了\N{\fs12}Cops picked him up... called me...and here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他想干嘛\N{\fs12}What does he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他想和他父亲生活在一起\N{\fs12}He wants to live with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但他不是华德·克里弗\N{\fs12}But he's not exactly Ward Cleaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,当他们在一起生活时  他曾经打了卢克的妈妈\N{\fs12}He used to beat up Luke's mother when they were living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,杰伊  他就像我最好的朋友\N{\fs12}Jay? He's like my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经\N{\fs12}Was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,警察撤销了对你的所有指控  卢克\N{\fs12}Police have dropped the charges against you, Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果你想  你可以回家了\N{\fs12}So if you want, you can go back to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过那个女士  我想和我父亲一起生活\N{\fs12}I told that lady I want to live with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对  好吧  我们会先和你父亲谈谈\N{\fs12}Right. Well, we'll have to speak to your father first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是有史以来最伟大的人  但至少他是个男人\N{\fs12}He's not the greatest person that's ever lived but... at least he's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜会带你去一个收容所\N{\fs12}Suzanne will take you to a shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那是在我们能想出该怎么做之前你能待的地方\N{\fs12}That's where you'll stay until we can figure out what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么好解决的\N{\fs12}What's there to figure out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈就是个婊子\N{\fs12}My mother's a whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  尼克\N{\fs12}Oh, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你不需要那么做的\N{\fs12}You know you didn't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那些花\N{\fs12}The flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么花\N{\fs12}Flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对  噢  我以为那是你\N{\fs12}Yeah. Oh. I thought that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,逗你呢\N{\fs12}I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我最喜欢百合花\N{\fs12}How'd you know I liked lilies so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你去年告诉我的  说在你心情很糟的时候\N{\fs12}Last year you told me that when you're in a bad mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢去农贸市场买白色的百合花\N{\fs12}you like to go to the Farmer's Market and buy white lilies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你能记得那件事真是贴心  谢谢你\N{\fs12}Well, it was sweet of you to remember that. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我在想  呃  如果你今晚不是很忙的话\N{\fs12}Uh... I was wondering, um...if you're not busy later tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想吃个晚餐\N{\fs12}if you want to get some dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我很乐意\N{\fs12}I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克·法林吗\N{\fs12}Nick Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,黛布拉·罗梅洛  我要和你谈谈我儿子卢克的事\N{\fs12}Debra Romello. I was told that you have my son Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我是他的律师\N{\fs12}Well, I'm his lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要见他\N{\fs12}I need to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他在收容所  - 在哪儿\N{\fs12}- He's at a shelter. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你需要打给社区服务中心去安排见面\N{\fs12}Well, you'll need to call Social Services to arrange a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是警察已经撤销对他的指控了  不是吗\N{\fs12}But the police have dropped the charges, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以他可以回家了吗  - 是的  他只是不想回去\N{\fs12}- So he can come home? - Yes he can. He just doesn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,打给社区服务中心\N{\fs12}Call Social Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你都没打电话\N{\fs12}You don't even call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你就\N{\fs12}You just--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  我的天  小杰克\N{\fs12}Oh, my God, Jakey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对  没有很严重  真的\N{\fs12}Yeah, it's not that bad, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了\N{\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我被  一个  一个白痴  抢劫了昨晚\N{\fs12}I got... Some... some idiot... robbed me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,打劫你吗\N{\fs12}Robbed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对  但这不是什么大事  真的\N{\fs12}Yeah. But it's no big deal, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  等下  老天  妈  我完全忘了买卖的事\N{\fs12}Oh... wait. God, Ma. I totally forgot about the closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  我们把它推迟到明天了\N{\fs12}It's okay. We pushed it back to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,买家们都很心烦  但是  我不相信有人\N{\fs12}The buyer's all upset, but... I can't believe someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,够了  好吗\N{\fs12}Enough, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我  - 抱歉  我没事  没事\N{\fs12}- I'm-- - Sorry. I'm fine. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  妈  我晚点有个会议  好吗\N{\fs12}Look, Ma, I'm late for a meeting, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  呃  没什么事好担心的  真的\N{\fs12}So, um, there's nothing to worry about. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,晚点我会打你电话谈  谈关于明天买卖的事\N{\fs12}I'm gonna call you later about that... about that closing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗  谢了  妈\N{\fs12}Okay? Thanks, Ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么预约到这儿的\N{\fs12}How did you get a reservation here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  跟D管家预约了\N{\fs12}l, uh, talked to the Maitre d'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  你知道  我为什么想吃晚餐的原因  呃\N{\fs12}Uh, you know, the reason why I wanted to have dinner, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要想想怎么解决\N{\fs12}We need to figure out how this is going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的事\N{\fs12}With the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对  好吧  我  我猜\N{\fs12}Right. Well, l-- I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很大一部分情况  都取决于我们会怎样\N{\fs12}a lot of that depends on what's going on with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs12}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们需要制定  特点的条款\N{\fs12}I think that we need to make... certain provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,比如呢\N{\fs12}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  有许多事情需要去考虑\N{\fs12}Well, there's a lot of things to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  呃  先从  钱开始\N{\fs12}Um... uh, money... for starters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,抚养一个情况特殊的孩子是非常昂贵的\N{\fs12}Raising a special needs child is very expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我想建立一个信托基金\N{\fs12}I would like to create a trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就不用去担心了\N{\fs12}Just so I don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你同意吗\N{\fs12}You agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果  如果那是你想的话\N{\fs12}lf... if that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对  那\N{\fs12}Yeah. That--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我迟到了\N{\fs12}Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  呃  我没有太多时间\N{\fs12}So, uh, I don't have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那  - 请坐\N{\fs12}- So... - Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,像我在电话里说的  我们抓住了这个家伙  汤姆·阿达斯\N{\fs12}Like I said on the phone, we picked up this guy Tom Addas
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在盛石用了你的信用卡\N{\fs12}using your Visa card over at Lightstone's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs12}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在十分钟里买了大概价值两千美元的衣服\N{\fs12}Bought about two thousand dollars' worth of clothes in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,先让你看看能不能认出他\N{\fs12}Just want to see if you recognize him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁看着熟悉吗\N{\fs12}Anyone look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一个都没有吗\N{\fs12}No one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看到他\N{\fs12}I don't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这个在右上角的家伙怎么样\N{\fs12}How about the guy in the upper right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这个吗\N{\fs12}This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  如果有那个混蛋对我做了他对你做的事\N{\fs12}You know, if some punk did to me what he did to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那  我们可以结束了吗\N{\fs12}So... are we done here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,儿童收容所\N{\fs12}Children's Shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,卢克\N{\fs12}Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你怎么样了  孩子\N{\fs12}Hey, how ya doing, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你长大了\N{\fs12}You're gettin' big.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在打橄榄球吗\N{\fs12}Playing football?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,足球\N{\fs12}Soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  不管怎样  那  呃  我觉得你和我\N{\fs12}Well, anyway, so, uh... I think this'll be good,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,住在一起挺好的\N{\fs12}me and you living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,会很有趣\N{\fs12}It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对  呃  你知道  你得换学校之类的\N{\fs12}Yeah, um... You know, you're gonna have to change schools and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那没事\N{\fs12}but that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我  我现在有女朋友了  卡莉\N{\fs12}And I got... I got a girlfriend now. Carly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你会喜欢她的\N{\fs12}You'll like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她还是个好厨子\N{\fs12}She's a good cook too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  我不再喝酒了  所以事情都会变好的\N{\fs12}Look I'm not drinking anymore... so things are gonna be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,更加平静\N{\fs12}A little more calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那你还有什么问题或者其他的吗\N{\fs12}So you got any questions or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  没有\N{\fs12}Uh... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,卢克\N{\fs12}Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你想和你爸住在一起吗\N{\fs12}Are you sure you want to live with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:13:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那  呃  我猜这事过去不久后我会再见到你  呃\N{\fs12}So, uh... I guess I'll see ya soon after all this, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  社区服务中心的手续已经完成了\N{\fs12}you know, Social Services stuff is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,皮特\N{\fs12}Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  我太想你了  宝贝\N{\fs12}Oh, I've missed you so much, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 太想  太想了  - 放开我\N{\fs12}- Mm, so, so much. - Get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怪你乱发脾气  宝贝\N{\fs12}I don't blame you for being upset, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有乱发脾气\N{\fs12}I'm not upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对  你没有  没事的  如果你觉得那是真的发生了就发生了\N{\fs12}Yes, you are, and it's okay if what you think happened really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,杰伊的父母在闹离婚\N{\fs12}Jay's parents are getting a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢\N{\fs12}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那不容易\N{\fs12}So it's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你经历过的\N{\fs12}You went through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他  他当时很伤心\N{\fs12}He... He was feeling sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他来找我\N{\fs12}He came at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他吻了我  然后我不知道怎么处理  你就进来了\N{\fs12}He kissed me... and l-- I didn't know how to react... and you walked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,卢克  我原谅了你对我做的事\N{\fs12}Luke, I forgive you for what you did to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不是真的想伤害我\N{\fs12}I know you didn't mean to hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,卢克\N{\fs12}Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不告诉你的律师你想回家\N{\fs12}Why don't you tell your lawyer you want to come home?
