Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.40,0:29:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那个烤箱  它是个神奇的传送工具\N{\fs12}The oven... It's one of those fancy convection things,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.76,0:29:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而且它花费  好像  大约  我不懂  不管你煮什么东西\N{\fs12}and it takes, like, about, I don't know, twenty-five percent less time
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.06,0:29:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都少花了二十五分钟因为它的这个风扇\N{\fs12}to cook whatever you're cooking because it's got this fan...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.42,0:29:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  妈  我  呃  我没有被抢劫\N{\fs12}You know, Ma, l, um...I didn't just get mugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.33,0:29:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\fs12}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.27,0:30:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,事情比抢劫更糟\N{\fs12}It was worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.91,0:30:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么更糟\N{\fs12}Worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.41,0:30:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那个家伙  他  呃  他做了一些事\N{\fs12}That guy, he, uh... he did certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.17,0:30:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fs12}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.48,0:30:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一些事\N{\fs12}Certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.60,0:30:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  杰克\N{\fs12}Oh, Jake...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.82,0:30:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我没事  好吗\N{\fs12}l-- I'm fine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.22,0:30:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs12}l...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.15,0:30:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是需要告诉某人真相  就这样  有关发生的一切\N{\fs12}I just need to tell someone the truth, that's all, about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.48,0:30:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  最糟的是  在你知道之前\N{\fs12}You know, the best part is that... before you know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.26,0:30:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,整个城市就都会知道发生了什么  我发生的那些\N{\fs12}the entire city's gonna know what happened. That I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.47,0:30:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,人们就是喜欢悲剧  你知道吗\N{\fs12}People just love a tragedy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.22,0:30:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,试着表现出他们的心碎和同情心\N{\fs12}Trying to be all heartbroken and sympathetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.37,0:30:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们心底里就是喜欢这样\N{\fs12}but deep down they just love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.52,0:30:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们一些谈资和笑料\N{\fs12}Gives 'em something to talk about and laugh about.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.27,0:30:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs12}Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.68,0:30:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让这家伙谈论发生的事\N{\fs12}I cannot have this guy talking about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.23,0:30:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是不能\N{\fs12}I just can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.49,0:31:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,匹兹堡是个小地方  妈\N{\fs12}Pittsburgh's a tiny place, Ma.
