Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.56,0:31:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  你想  你想喝一杯或者别的什么吗\N{\fs12}That's all right. You want a... you want a drink or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.64,0:31:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  不  不  不  不了  谢谢\N{\fs12}Oh, no, no, no. No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.63,0:31:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是  呃  呃  我需要和你聊些事\N{\fs12}I just, um... Um, I needed to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.28,0:31:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  怎么了\N{\fs12}Sure. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.98,0:31:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  我没有被抢劫\N{\fs12}l, um... I didn't get mugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.18,0:31:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.40,0:31:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是一起性侵犯\N{\fs12}It was a sexual assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.40,0:31:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\fs12}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.84,0:31:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我在俱乐部遇见一个男人  一起喝了点酒\N{\fs12}I met a guy at a club. Had a few drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.88,0:31:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,走回汽车旅馆\N{\fs12}Went back to a motel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.32,0:31:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,事情就失去了控制\N{\fs12}It got out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.86,0:31:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  呃  警察捉到了那个家伙  然后他们试图操纵他\N{\fs12}The, uh... police caught the guy, and they're trying to manipulate him
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.41,0:31:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为越轨性交进行认罪协商\N{\fs12}into a plea bargain for deviate sexual intercourse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.92,0:31:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs12}My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.27,0:31:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天  我\N{\fs12}My God. l--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.15,0:31:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么现在才告诉我\N{\fs12}Why are you telling me this now?
