Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.24,0:32:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs12}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.74,0:32:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.61,0:32:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  杰克\N{\fs12}I don't know, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.49,0:32:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\fs12}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.03,0:32:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.50,0:32:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  伯顿\N{\fs12}Thank you, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.11,0:32:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.34,0:32:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  宝贝\N{\fs12}Hey, sweetie. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.77,0:32:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  抱歉  宝贝  我忍不住\N{\fs12}Oh, I'm sorry, baby. I can't help it.
