Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.07,0:32:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我朋友鲍比准备把DVD放进去\N{\fs12}Yeah. My friend Bobby's gonna put the DVD in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.08,0:33:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都准备好了  - 谢了\N{\fs12}- Be ready to go. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.50,0:33:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  好了  宝贝\N{\fs12}Uh... all right, sweetie.
