Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.17,0:33:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那天你回到家的时候\N{\fs12}The other day when you came home...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.09,0:33:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你  呃\N{\fs12}you were, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.81,0:33:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,当你  当你足球训练回来的时候\N{\fs12}When-- when you went to soccer practice
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.99,0:33:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你所有的朋友都很高兴\N{\fs12}and you were having fun with all your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.87,0:33:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然后杰伊停了下来\N{\fs12}and Jay stopped by...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.55,0:33:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始交谈\N{\fs12}we started talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.02,0:33:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  我们  呃\N{\fs12}and... then... we, uh...
