Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.40,0:33:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没和任何人说\N{\fs12}Not to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.00,0:33:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有\N{\fs12}And I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.48,0:33:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的秘密\N{\fs12}It will be our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.45,0:33:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,卢克\N{\fs12}Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.47,0:33:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都会犯错\N{\fs12}Everyone makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.65,0:33:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,杰伊说他没告诉任何人是吗\N{\fs12}Jay said he won't tell anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.28,0:33:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对  对  他保证过\N{\fs12}Yeah. Yeah, he promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.13,0:34:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.10,0:34:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉了他真相  我照你说的做了\N{\fs12}I told him the truth. I did what you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.56,0:34:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有约定的\N{\fs12}We had a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.39,0:34:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她在说什么\N{\fs12}What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.59,0:34:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是杰伊\N{\fs12}It wasn't just Jay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.57,0:34:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.52,0:34:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.08,0:34:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  你可以做唯一的受托人  但是  呃  我需要你签一下这个\N{\fs12}Uh, you can be sole trustee, but, uh, I'll need you to sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.49,0:34:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一份保管同意书吗\N{\fs12}A custody agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.99,0:34:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我只是想确保宝宝出生后我能得到保护\N{\fs12}Well, I just want to make sure that I'm protected after the baby's born.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.71,0:34:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.70,0:34:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要法律和身体上的共同监护权  仅此而已\N{\fs12}I want joint legal and physical custody, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.82,0:35:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是一笔交易  你知道  我不想用这个来谈判\N{\fs12}This is not a deal, you know. I'm not negotiating this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.99,0:35:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你只是想让我做你的银行  是这样吗\N{\fs12}So you just want me to be your bank? That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.04,0:35:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我只是想保证我能不依靠你\N{\fs12}No. I just want to make sure that I can provide for our child
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.76,0:35:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,来保护我们的孩子  这非常简单\N{\fs12}without having to depend on you. It's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.99,0:35:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,简单吗  你觉得这简单吗\N{\fs12}Simple? You think this is simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.31,0:35:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,被告诉说不能信任我抚养自己的孩子吗\N{\fs12}Being told that I can't be trusted to raise my own child?
