Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.59,0:35:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我\N{\fs12}No, I did--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.23,0:35:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.30,0:35:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那我想我们今晚不用一起吃饭了\N{\fs12}So I assume we're not gonna have dinner tonight now.
