Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.24,0:35:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我就是想如果你\N{\fs12}Well, I just thought that if you...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.78,0:35:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,露露  我们可以解决这个问题  好吗  我没有在担心\N{\fs12}Lulu, we're gonna work through this, okay? I'm not worried.
