Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.88,0:36:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然  他们确实想要这个狗娘养的\N{\fs12}Apparently, they really want to get this son of a bitch,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.27,0:36:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有没有你的帮助\N{\fs12}with your help or without.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.16,0:36:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Right.
