Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.54,0:36:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs12}Uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.46,0:36:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我就是很抱歉那个  呃  我把你牵扯进来\N{\fs12}Yeah, I'm-- I'm just so sorry that, uh, I got you involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.92,0:36:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  我都不知道这是怎么发生的\N{\fs12}l, uh... I don't really even know how this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.30,0:36:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  但是  呃  所以我想说我觉得能和你工作很幸运  伯顿\N{\fs12}Uhm... But, uh... So I say I feel very fortunate to work with you, Burton,
