Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.62,0:36:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  我向你保证  我再也不会让我的原因使这家律师事务所\N{\fs12}And... you have my word that I will never put myself in a position
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.16,0:36:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有名声败坏的风险\N{\fs12}to discredit this law firm ever again.
