Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.90,0:38:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要谈谈\N{\fs12}We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.10,0:38:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好  怎么了\N{\fs12}Okay. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.62,0:38:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉地方检察官  事情已经结束了\N{\fs12}You tell the DA the deaI's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.06,0:38:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你是无辜的  为什么要接受认罪协商\N{\fs12}You're innocent. Why accept a plea bargain?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.03,0:38:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对  但是他们说  - 他们撒谎\N{\fs12}- Yeah, but they said that... - They're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.69,0:38:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没有我他们什么都得不到  我还什么都没说\N{\fs12}Without me they got nothing, and I ain't talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.11,0:38:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,对  没错  我什么都没说\N{\fs12}Yeah, that's right. I'm not gonna say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.42,0:38:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你去告诉你的律师说不行\N{\fs12}So you tell your lawyer no deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.67,0:38:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要问为什么  就说不行\N{\fs12}Don't say why. Just say no deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.91,0:38:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗\N{\fs12}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.16,0:39:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我发现  我因为你染病\N{\fs12}And if I find out that I'm sick because of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.81,0:39:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我会杀了你\N{\fs12}I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.01,0:39:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算做什么\N{\fs12}How're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.60,0:39:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我需要告诉法官你想去哪儿生活\N{\fs12}You know, I need to tell the judge where you want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.41,0:39:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.76,0:39:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  所以如果你想你可以待在收容所\N{\fs12}Okay. So you can stay in the shelter if you'd like,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.80,0:39:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我可以试着帮你找个寄养家庭\N{\fs12}or I can try and find you a foster family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.03,0:39:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那也许会花些时间  但是\N{\fs12}It may take some time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.66,0:39:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想了很多我妈妈独自生活的事\N{\fs12}I just think my mother's by herself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.87,0:39:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,当你一个人的时候事情很容易出事  你知道吗\N{\fs12}Things happen when you're alone, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.55,0:39:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不在那儿了  事情只会变得更糟\N{\fs12}lf I'm not there, it'll only make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.98,0:39:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\fs12}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.92,0:39:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得她还会这么做吗\N{\fs12}Think she'll do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.53,0:39:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可能\N{\fs12}Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.66,0:39:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想去什么随意的寄养家庭\N{\fs12}I'm just not that into having some random foster family
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.54,0:39:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们假装接受我  你知道吗\N{\fs12}pretending to be into me... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.49,0:39:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你想和你妈一起住吗\N{\fs12}You want to live with your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.30,0:40:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对  - 好吧\N{\fs12}- Yeah. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.15,0:40:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就这么和法官说\N{\fs12}That's what I'll tell the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.81,0:40:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.94,0:40:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰克\N{\fs12}Jakey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.85,0:40:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs12}Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.09,0:40:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干嘛  很晚了\N{\fs12}What're you doing here? It's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.88,0:40:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡不着\N{\fs12}I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.94,0:40:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  新的公寓  我不知道\N{\fs12}You know, the new apartment... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.73,0:40:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它  呃  所有东西都太他妈干净了\N{\fs12}It's, uh... everything's so damn clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.65,0:40:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\fs12}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.34,0:40:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备出去吗\N{\fs12}Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.22,0:40:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  小杰克  我真的很担心你\N{\fs12}Ooh, Jakey, I'm really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.42,0:40:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你什么意思\N{\fs12}Well... what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.37,0:40:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很多事你都不告诉我  比如你去哪儿了  去做什么\N{\fs12}There are things that you don't tell me, like where you go and what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.56,0:40:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那都无所谓  我知道这是你的生活\N{\fs12}That's fine. I know it's your life and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.76,0:40:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我是你妈妈  我会害怕\N{\fs12}but I'm your mother and I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.20,0:40:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  宝贝\N{\fs12}Listen, honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.73,0:40:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以告诉我真相\N{\fs12}you can tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.97,0:40:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  是吗\N{\fs12}You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.44,0:40:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂\N{\fs12}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.78,0:41:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs12}Ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.02,0:41:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好说的\N{\fs12}There's nothing to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.21,0:41:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我今晚真的很高兴\N{\fs12}Well, I had a really nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.14,0:41:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs12}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.21,0:41:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs12}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.39,0:41:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那  我  我想  明天见吧\N{\fs12}So... l... I guess I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.21,0:41:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不信任我\N{\fs12}I know you don't trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.39,0:41:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我没怪你\N{\fs12}I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.86,0:41:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不想放弃\N{\fs12}But I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.21,0:41:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  如果你想的话  你可以叫我去死 但是我不想放弃\N{\fs12}I mean, you can tell me to go to hell if you want, but I'm not gonna give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.19,0:41:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fs12}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.37,0:41:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.66,0:42:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  那个  呃  我们讨论的问题\N{\fs12}Burton, that, uh, problem we discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.05,0:42:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.24,0:42:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,已经被解决了\N{\fs12}It's been resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.57,0:42:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 解决了吗  - 对\N{\fs12}- Resolved? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.26,0:42:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就像从没发生过一样\N{\fs12}So it's like it never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.55,0:42:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Good.
